*ConsoleMatrix*
is simple way to enjoy matrix. Just download EXE file and run!
Possible arguments:
troll >> Enables troll mode, none of the keys will function (only for this program!).

Keys:
R - Manually invokes resize function (may be buggy on windows)
+ - Decreases speed of steps
- - Increses speed of steps (Maximum speed is about 1000 steps/ second)
ESC - Exits program
